Node:	bvr_near_far (Speech response to person getting too close)
Input:
	None
Config: 
	from srv_sonar:
		proximity < 100cm 	"Near"
					o/w 	"Far"
Output:
	String near_far ["Near", "Far"]
Steps:
	1. Initialization: Being subscribing to tpc_sonar (10Hz)
	2. if proximity is <= to 30cm then:
		(a) near_far = "You are getting too close"
		(b) send request to srv_speaker (near_far)
